#. Access Control - AdminSettings.php
#: includes/Controllers/AdminSettings.php
msgid "Control who can access Knowledge Base content. These are global defaults that can be overridden at the collection and article level."
msgstr "控制誰可以存取知識庫內容。這些是全域預設值，可在集合和文章層級覆寫。"

#: includes/Controllers/AdminSettings.php
msgid "Enable Access Control"
msgstr "啟用存取控制"

#: includes/Controllers/AdminSettings.php
