msgstr "這設定了所有知識庫內容的基本存取層級。個別集合和文章可以有更嚴格的限制。"

#: includes/Controllers/AdminSettings.php
msgid "Access Denied Message"
msgstr "存取拒絕訊息"

#: includes/Controllers/AdminSettings.php
